The '''udjudg''' was a special [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument played by the [[Zybahhod Yenyoni]]. They were uniquely suited to play it with their "Y"-shaped naso-facial openings.<ref name="DAA">{{GalaxyCite|7|Design An Alien}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The udjudg was created by [[Jennifer Kay]], a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan, for the backstory of her [[Zybahhod Yenyoni]] entry in the ''[[Design An Alien]]'' contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''.<ref name="DAA" />

